                            <comment id="17985855" author="krummas" created="Tue, 24 Jun 2025 12:34:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch in PR implements Benedicts suggestion from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-14554&quot; title=&quot;Streaming needs to synchronise access to LifecycleTransaction&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-14554&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-14554&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; by giving each incoming file its own LifecycleTransaction and then as the stream finishes we atomically hand over each file to a &quot;parent&quot; transaction&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="18003910" author="maedhroz" created="Tue, 8 Jul 2025 21:58:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Approved in the PR w/ a couple nits in &lt;tt&gt;SSTableTxnSingleStreamWriter&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
